Create Food drops mush; Sleep II adjacent / Sleep III all in sight; Identify fully
IDs an item; Fire Bolt 9d8; Slow −1 speed unit.

--[ Mages' Guide to Power ]--------------------------------------------------

```
Spell            Mage Lv/Mn/Fl/Xp   Ranger          Rogue
Frost Ball       19 12 55 38       27 21 65 22      --
Recharge II      21 12 90 44       29 23 95 23      --
Teleport Other   23 12 60 50       31 25 70 25      --
Haste Self       25 12 65 63       33 25 75 38      --
Fire Ball        29 18 65 88       35 25 80 50      --
Word Destruct.   33 21 80 125      37 30 95 100     --
Genocide         37 25 95 200      --               --
```

Frost Ball 48 / Fire Ball 72 at center; Haste +1 speed for 1d20+level turns;
Word of Destruction nukes the area; Genocide kills one letter-group.

--[ Recharging ]-------------------------------------------------------------

```
Survive chance ≈ (origin_bonus + 50 − wand/staff_level − charges) / 10
  origin_bonus: Recharge I = 20; Recharge II / scroll = 60
  Destroyed 1 time in Chance

Charges added: 2 + (1..max)
  max = origin_bonus / (2 + item_level) + 1
```

